3. Concept Stress-Testing Engine

Before adopting an idea, run it through automated questions:
	•	Where does it fail?
	•	What assumptions break it?
	•	What would falsify it?
	•	What domain contradicts it?

Think of it like an intellectual crash test lab.

Impact: ⭐⭐⭐⭐
Feasibility: ⭐⭐⭐⭐

⸻

